Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 14
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 12
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 15
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: From the publisher: "With Itachi having stopped Kabuto, itâ€™s time for the Edotensei warriors to finally be returned to the afterlife."
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 61
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: A boy named Sora is separated from his friends and crosses paths with Donald Duck and Goofy who are searching for Mickey Mouse.
Title: KINGDOM HEARTS, FINAL MIX, VOL. 1
Author: Shiro Amano

Description: Talk about a complicated life: a male high school student is murdered, then becomes a zombie, and is then transformed into a magical girl.
Title: IS THIS A ZOMBIE?, VOL. 5
Author: Shinichi Kimura and Sacchi

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2

Description: A boy named Roxas encounters strange creatures and is plagued by strange dreams. How will this lead to a boy named Sora, Donald Duck and Goofy?
Title: KINGDOM HEARTS II, VOL. 1
Author: Shiro Amano
